---
title: Fragrant Aubergine and Chicken Curry with Chickpeas, Coconut Rice and Nigella Seeds
description: Onion marmalade in a curry?! Well that, is the secret ingredient to this delicious recipe. We're all about thinking outside the box (!), so when Ellie, our menu planner said she'd like the chefs to create a recipe using our trackelments onion marmalade, Mimi went rogue and decided aubergine curry it was. After some doubt from Andre and Liz, they tasted it and agreed the onion marmalade was the glue that brought the whole thing together!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/fragrant-aubergine-and-chicken-curry-27f6479a-5a3b8346.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/fragrant-aubergine-and-chicken-curry-5fc1125aee0f354f584ea6f0-62b38f91.pdf
time required: 40 minutes
